Title: Integrated notification plugin for mobile phone push messages via Pushover
Level: 1
Component: notifications
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.7i3
Date: 1437379476
Class: feature

We already had a notfication plugin in the treasures directory which was very limited
in the features and was not configurable via WATO. The new plugin provides much more
details in the notifications and can now be configured via the GUI.
